Fix some warnings found during Code Analysis.
Fix more warnings found during Code Analysis.
Fix yet more warnings found during Code Analysis.
Fixed as many warnings as possible. Down to 52.
3.1.5 Added exportDb() method. Exports an accessable file on the Tablet.
3.1.7 Added import method. Backup/Restore seems to work on Tablet.
3.1.9 Fix bug in OwnedDetailsActivity where deleted block comes back when new block is added. This bug wasn't related to the recent refactoring/cleanup.
3.2.3 Add feature to email backed up DB.
